snippet.title: Floodland - Announcement Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Floodland, Vile Monarch's post-climate apocalypse city builder, was revealed during the Gamescom Future Games Show. Paddles at the ready, as Floodlands is coming to PC on November 15, 2022.
